      "id": "hk_box_b",
      "x": 140,
      "y": 1555,
      "width": 1058,
      "height": 190,
      "text": "Fire automatically \u2014 no manual invocation:\n\nPreToolUse  \u2192  pre_tool_use.py\n  Blocks: rm -rf, DROP TABLE, force-push\n  Blocks: .env file access\n\nPostToolUse (Write|Edit)\n  \u2192  post_tool_use.py  (validation)\n  \u2192  ruff_validator.py  (Python lint)\n  \u2192  ty_validator.py  (type checking)\n\nSessionEnd\n  \u2192  session_end.py  (state persist)\n  \u2192  post_agent_contract_validator.py",
      "originalText": "Fire automatically \u2014 no manual invocation:\n\nPreToolUse  \u2192  pre_tool_use.py\n  Blocks: rm -rf, DROP TABLE, force-push\n  Blocks: .env file access\n\nPostToolUse (Write|Edit)\n  \u2192  post_tool_use.py  (validation)\n  \u2192  ruff_validator.py  (Python lint)\n  \u2192  ty_validator.py  (type checking)\n\nSessionEnd\n  \u2192  session_end.py  (state persist)\n  \u2192  post_agent_contract_validator.py",
